" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大部分勇武都係和理非進化，只係差在進化速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5個月黎最大優勢係因為冇大台，狗拉唔曬，同樣，無論今日定以後都唔會有大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗提出的核心示威者概念係不存在的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，散水認輸就係衰比對家睇，唔係要咁柒啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"53fc073f15fad558d1b87146173a7143a24625a8","tid":1732520,"uid":217336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b69a3454300268364591c4676087c34d994a89df","tid":1732520,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:07:05.000Z","msg":"習近平幾多歲呀<br />\n仲玩到幾多年<br />\n使唔使叫人研發長生不老藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:28:17.000Z","msg":"睇下老江，亞視死左佢都仲未死呀<br />\n習大起碼玩多廿年，到時香港已經變左臭港"},{"pid":"ef3b6c01dde4a4ac4b1571b20332054d1225d741","tid":1732520,"uid":49699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:28:45.000Z","msg":"郭文貴以前掌情報...佢講D 野多多少少有根據"},{"pid":"a3980a04ca9a136cce13c4cce1dd8fb853c9e885","tid":1732520,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:30:37.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢已經firm左佢係尻Up之王"},{"pid":"b8cb8a0fe3fc28e54998d287b37f4bdefd08525c","tid":1732520,"uid":200495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:32:17.000Z","msg":"吹水怪又出現 已經斬咗幾刀啦喎 拔刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"57039f81358edbd0d